		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.madelinedowney.com/2011/06/my-first-story/" />
		<id>http://www.madelinedowney.com/?p=457</id>
		<updated>2011-06-22T04:04:08Z</updated>
		<published>2011-06-22T04:04:08Z</published>
		<category scheme="http://www.madelinedowney.com" term="Rants" />		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[Ghostwriter&#8217;s note: I&#8217;ve had a hard time deciding what to do with this site now that Maddie is old enough to speak for herself. Turns out, I&#8217;m out of a job! What follows is her first written story, as transcribed by her mom. —JD Context &#8220;Sodo&#8221; is Maddie&#8217;s favorite fabricated word. This story was told [...]]]></summary>
		<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.madelinedowney.com/2011/06/my-first-story/"><![CDATA[<p><em>Ghostwriter&#8217;s note: I&#8217;ve had a hard time deciding what to do with this site now that Maddie is old enough to speak for herself. Turns out, I&#8217;m out of a job! What follows is her first written story, as transcribed by her mom. —JD</em></p>
<h2>Context</h2>
<p>&#8220;Sodo&#8221; is Maddie&#8217;s favorite fabricated word. This story was told while playing with a new <a href="http://www.gummylump.com/p/ExpressionsStamperSet/2450">stamp set</a> that features emotional faces.</a></p>
<h2>The Story</h2>
<p>There was an angry stamp.</p>
<p><img src="http://www.madelinedowney.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/angry.jpg" alt="" title="angry" width="200" height="166" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-458" /></p>
<p>And the others were not sad.<br />
That one is happy.</p>
<p><img src="http://www.madelinedowney.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/happy.jpg" alt="" title="happy" width="200" height="206" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-459" /></p>
<p>They go to their house and they have people there.<br />
Then they sleep in the bedrooms.<br />
This one&#8217;s bedroom and his bedroom and his bedroom&#8230;</p>
<p><em>[she mumbles something about the Moon and tries to draw one. I wrote the word "MOON" and she wrote it too! —KK]</em><br />
<img src="http://www.madelinedowney.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/moon.jpg" alt="" title="moon" width="300" height="107" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-460" /></p>
<p>When they sleep, when they heard a noise.  A bird.<br />
They climbed on it.<br />
When they heard a noise, this was another tweet.<br />
When they go on a Sodo, that&#8217;s the end!!</p>
<p>Now they heard another noise.<br />
When they climbed on it, they begin to cry.<br />
And Maddie&#8217;s here. And said Maddie be careful with the stamps!<br />
They get on the bird when they heard a noise.<br />
They say, &#8220;I wanna go home.&#8221;<br />
Then they heard another noise, then they can go on their Sodo.<br />
They begin to cry.</p>
<p>The Sodo is yellow.<br />
When they heard a noise, like this <em>[scribbles her marker really fast]</em>.<br />
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Froggy-Goes-Doctor-Jonathan-London/dp/0142401935/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&#038;qid=1308713709&#038;sr=8-1">Froggy goes to the doctor</a> with his mommy and sister and daddy.<br />
Doctor&#8217;s name is Adios.<br />
When they begin to cry a little, poor guys!!!<br />
They don&#8217;t have to be sleepy &#8211; they just have to tell mommy&#8217;s and daddo&#8217;s.<br />
When they go on a Sodo, they leave.<br />
They go home.<br />
They make some dinner.</p>
]]></content>
